subSubSection.paragraph:
Preliminary Conservation Status
— 
Solanum piluliferum

is considered of least concern (
LC
) due to its relatively wide distribution (EOO: 
202,475 km
2
), abundant populations and numerous collections across the distribution range, although the small area of occupancy (AOO: 
188 km
2
) suggests that it would merit being treated as endangered (
EN
) (
IUCN 2016
).
